py manage.py createsuperuser: Creates a super user.

.\env\Scripts\activate: Activates the env file. Whatever tf that means. Wait I actually might know. But run this 
before running the server. Or it won't work.

py manage.py runserver: Runs the server

pip install -r requirements.txt.: Installs dependencies. Might not need the trailing .

pip install --upgrade pip: I think this updates python for you.